           move      zero                 to   w-gen-ctr-err          .
       exe-reg-orc-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione file guida                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Wait di un secondo                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mwait0"                         .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open file guida ON                          *
