      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Valore in uscita                        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rn-orc-ndo-num-doc   to   w-att-orc-ndo-num      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     att-orc-ndo-999.
       att-orc-ndo-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se numero documento passato a non zero :    *
      *                  * uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     att-orc-ndo-999.
       att-orc-ndo-999.
           exit.
           
